Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.08,0:00:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello boys!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.12,0:00:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Hemione.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.50,0:00:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Erm, well, I'm heading home for a winter holliday for a few weeks,\Nbut ahm, before I go I -- I'd just wanted to give this to you guys.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh!\N-Happy christmas!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.08,0:00:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wonder what it is.\N- I wonder, what this could be...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.13,0:00:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- I hope it's a puppy!\N- Puppy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.63,0:00:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Puppy! Puppy! Puppy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- A book?!?\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.42,0:00:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross! Merry christmas, Ron!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.81,0:00:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.39,0:00:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, no! No, wait! It's not just any book!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.14,0:00:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a scrapbook! I made it of all of our\Nmemories of our first semester in Hogwarts!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... oh yeah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.73,0:00:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,See, here's... ah... here's tickets from the hogwarts express,\Nand ah... here is a clipping from the prophet about that\NQuidditchgame that you guys won last month.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.83,0:00:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A yeah... Remus Lupin eats shit. Gryffindor wins.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.04,0:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- Merry christmas, Ron!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.30,0:00:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry christmas to you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.01,0:00:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.63,0:01:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hermione, why is here a... a clipping\Nin here from the prophet about Sirius Black?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they mentioned Harry in it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.44,0:01:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!...ah...Oh!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.63,0:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Before his escape from Azkaban Sirius Black went on\Nthe record saying: I'm wanna find Harry Potter - that's you -
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.93,0:01:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I wanna drug and kill him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.12,0:01:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you nervous, Harry? He IS a murderer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.01,0:01:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. I mean, I live at Hogwarts!\NAnd it's an impenetrable fortress.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.51,0:01:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't think any of us have to worry any old thing about...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.91,0:01:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius Blaaaaaack!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.45,0:01:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius Blaaaaaaaaaaack!...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.27,0:01:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Check mate! Sirius Blahahahahack!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.17,0:01:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What about him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He was spotted by the paintings on the third floor!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.67,0:01:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The dogs playing poker peed on the carpet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.73,0:01:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The screaming man has never looked more terrified!\NIt took the entire last supper to calm him down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.75,0:01:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius Black -- has broken into our castle!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.80,0:01:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet! Quiet! Quieeeet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.99,0:02:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you yell it only makes Sirius wanna kill you faster!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.09,0:02:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now prefects, escort these kiddies\Nto their dorm to tuck them in!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.76,0:02:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The teachers and I will search\Nthe entire castle for Sirius Black.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.89,0:02:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Siruis Black! Sirius Black! That bastard!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.69,0:02:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna find him and I'm gonna throw everything --\Neverything I know at him! I'm talking about:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.73,0:02:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...lumos, alohomora, jellylegs jinx, everything...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, you're better then that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.54,0:02:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll jellylegs jinx him!\N- [scream]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, that almost hit me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a rage!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the maddest I've ever been!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.75,0:02:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz Sirius Black took everything away from me,\Nhe took my parents, my whole life, everything!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna find him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,With this. -- The Maraunders Map!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.72,0:02:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I think Sirius is in here, but it could be wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very complicantiomatic.\N[??? complicated schematic ???]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.20,0:03:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about this, Harry. This room is really forbidden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.15,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry... I'm full frightened.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.24,0:03:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! D'you hear that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.46,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen you in a dream,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.94,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,an old familiar scene, from somewhere...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's glowing in your eyes,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.81,0:03:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know and recognize, from somewhere...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Those voices,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.43,0:04:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,singing out,\N"La, la, la, la, la..."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.21,0:04:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Lily & James] La, la, la, la, la...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.09,0:04:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Harry, Lily, James] La, la, la, la, la... la.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see them?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.87,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.26,0:04:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All I see is myself and I'm inside\NWilly Wonka's chocolate factory.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermione is turning into a blueberry and I'm eating her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.08,0:04:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see myself turning into Cho Chang ya'll...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.44,0:04:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the mirror of erised, Harry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.23,0:04:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It shows you nothing more or less, then the\Ndeepest most desperate desire of your heart.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.33,0:04:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are your parents, Harry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry! Harry, watch out, that's Sirius Black!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, you bastard! Alohomora!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kids...\N- Jellylegs jinx!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Unjellify!\N- Oh! ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.28,0:05:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, he's too much for us!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I 've got one more thing. Lumos!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Expelliarmus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, just let me explain...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wanna explain?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- How you betrayed my parents and killed them?\N- No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.36,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't betray your parents and I've never killed anybody!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was framed!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.68,0:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved your parents, Harry!\NYour dad was my best friend!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I believe you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, Harry, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.94,0:05:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...when I look in that mirror I see them too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see them.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They were people that I loved,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you were barely old enough
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to be there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.86,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your mothers eyes,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.77,0:06:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath your dad's untidy dark hair.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.03,0:06:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Those voices,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.31,0:06:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,ringing out,\N"La, la, la, la, la..."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Lily & James] La, la, la, la, la...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.26,0:06:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sirius, Lily, James] La, la, la, la, la...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would never do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,anything that could hurt you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.57,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They were both my family!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all that's left of what I knew,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.93,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you must know somewhere it's true!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.85,0:06:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.04,0:06:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,those voies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.58,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,reaching out,\N"La, la, la, la, la..."
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.52,0:07:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Lilly, James] La, la, la, la, la...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.33,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Harry, Sirius, Lily, James] La, la, la, la, la...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.06,0:07:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Harry, Sirius, Lily, James] La.
